{"type":"article","id":21606,"title":"如果不会“说普通话”，还有机会“做文明人”吗？","uid":50245,"topics":[1415,442,1,351,1428,163],"contents":"“说普通话做文明人”是一句耳熟能详的推普口号，由此产生两个问题：<br>\n<br>\n1）如果普通话定义为北京官话的某种标准语，那么不会说普通话的人比如Tim Cook算不算文明人？<br>\n2）如果普通话定义为本国政府推广的官方语言，那么抗拒推普的马来西亚华教人士算不算文明人？<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ec8LOLOXgAcDDjd?format=png&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ec8LOLOXgAcDDjd?format=png&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ec8LOLOXgAcDDjd?format=png&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-15","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}